{"tid":1722350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TG毒不能解，可殘留身體超廿年","createTime":"2019-11-15T01:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T06:01:44.000Z","uid":331173,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a30fa23d42f6453808d214318de7edebccae730","tid":1722350,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:08:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">前線記者確診不治之症 正視催淚彈毒害刻不容緩</span></strong></span><br />\n<blockquote>導致氯痤瘡的類二噁英構造十分穩定，身體攝入後難以排出，而且無法分解，<span style=\"color: pink;\">它的毒性需長達廿年才減半</span>。</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>對於常身處前線、暴露於充滿催淚煙的環境之下工作的立場哥哥而言，<span style=\"color: pink;\">皮膚接觸是一個重要的接觸途徑</span>。如此，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">即使配戴面罩或呼吸器等保護裝備，身體也無法避免攝入類二噁英。</span></strong></span></blockquote><br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/前線記者確診不治之症-正視催淚彈毒害刻不容緩/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB%E4%B9%8B%E7%97%87-%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%96%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E6%AF%92%E5%AE%B3%E5%88%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E7%B7%A9%2F&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=99c1c348\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E4%B8%8D%E6%B2%BB%E4%B9%8B%E7%97%87-%E6%AD%A3%E8%A6%96%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E6%AF%92%E5%AE%B3%E5%88%BB%E4%B8%8D%E5%AE%B9%E7%B7%A9%2F&h=b31c361a\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/前線記者確診不治之症-正視催淚彈毒害刻不容緩/</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">載豬咀都無用，皮膚會吸收</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30QeVjF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30QeVjF.jpg&h=919822de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">著化學保護衣</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQ780HE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQ780HE.jpg&h=efc26aa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RPmmBfd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRPmmBfd.png&h=2be6b3ac&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ffZnVc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ffZnVc.jpg&h=3354ed80&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3EdW9Ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3EdW9Ad.jpg&h=51d47828&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2xujnVb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2xujnVb.jpg&h=adcb0889&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rbhpy1S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbhpy1S.jpg&h=c5b7121e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">載豬咀都無用，皮膚會吸收</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30QeVjF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30QeVjF.jpg&h=919822de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">著化學保護衣</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"589dfa58c8d0caf867aef14c2db2533e5f39a300","tid":1722350,"uid":141597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:09:11.000Z","msg":"[正視聽]邊撚個再話大學據點係鳩佔或者鼓吹棄守一律為風向分化撚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722290</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7277328a1e97c4a32743b5d63b561012077bf13c","tid":1722350,"uid":338362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:11:55.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"268f84cebc2e97b9af588013ec1e1d9419dfc686","tid":1722350,"uid":331173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:28:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>為何煤礦工人要帶雀仔入礦洞 雀仔死左就係警號</strong></span></span><br />\nSEARCH：Why do miners carry canaries?<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sentinel_species\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FSentinel_species&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=982501ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sentinel_species</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/story-real-canary-coal-mine-180961570/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smithsonianmag.com%2Fsmart-news%2Fstory-real-canary-coal-mine-180961570%2F&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=75e6352f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/story-real-canary-coal-mine-180961570/</a><br />\n<br />\n中文：<a href=\"http://mos.hk/maonshan/2/9/10\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmos.hk%2Fmaonshan%2F2%2F9%2F10&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjVznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=86dfffdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://mos.hk/maonshan/2/9/10</a><br />\n<blockquote>兩世紀前，美國西部的煤礦工人每天都攜帶一隻金絲雀（即石燕或白燕之類）入礦洞，因為這種鳥兒不僅喜歡鳴唱且聲音響亮。礦工若聽到礦洞內的鳥鳴聲，則表示洞內安全，反之則是危險警號。馬鞍山礦工亦仿效此法，因此大爆炸後礦工紛紛拿著鳥籠上班，蔚為奇觀</blockquote>"},{"pid":"492f2102e2d3d63a9a1b30ac1d369e4d215bbef4","tid":1722350,"uid":282891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:39:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">催淚彈係政府春袋<br />\n<br />\n快啲入呀</span></span><br />\n搵人同我瘋狂做文宣<br />\n<br />\n文宣升級：KO港豬必殺技曝光<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722528\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722528</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"186fbb4d5336a980e2bedb43956c0f30b876c97e","tid":1722350,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"492f2102e2d3d63a9a1b30ac1d369e4d215bb